<view class="page home-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view>
      <text class="eyebrow">Duck Travel Kit</text>
      <view class="hero-title">冲鸭去旅行</view>
      <view class="hero-subtitle">日程清单、旅行备忘、消费统计，一次出行的关键信息都放在这里。</view>
    </view>
    <button class="hero-action" bindtap="addTrip">新旅程</button>
  </view>

  <view wx:if="{{nextTrip}}" class="trip-strip panel">
    <view>
      <view class="trip-name">{{nextTrip.name}}</view>
      <view class="trip-date">{{nextTrip.destination}} · {{nextTrip.startDate}} - {{nextTrip.endDate}}</view>
    </view>
    <button class="strip-button" bindtap="openTrip" data-id="{{nextTrip.id}}">详情</button>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">
    <text>核心模块</text>
  </view>
  <view class="module-list">
    <button class="module-card panel schedule" bindtap="goSchedule">
      <view class="module-top">
        <text class="module-index">01</text>
        <text class="module-metric">{{scheduleCount}} 项</text>
      </view>
      <view class="module-title">日程清单</view>
      <view class="module-desc">以时间轴查看每日行程，包含景点、交通、住宿等安排。</view>
    </button>

    <button class="module-card panel memo" bindtap="goNotes">
      <view class="module-top">
        <text class="module-index">02</text>
        <text class="module-metric">{{memoDone}}/{{memoTotal}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="module-title">备忘</view>
      <view class="module-desc">添加旅行待办、提醒和注意事项，完成后可直接勾选。</view>
    </button>

    <button class="module-card panel expense" bindtap="goStats">
      <view class="module-top">
        <text class="module-index">03</text>
        <text class="module-metric">¥{{summary.expenseTotal}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="module-title">消费统计</view>
      <view class="module-desc">查看餐饮、交通、住宿、购物等分类占比，主支出为 {{topCategory}}。</view>
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
